had been ordered from Bohn by Gilmer and listed in Kean’s 1825 catalog.<sup>62</sup> Evidence for this filiation via selective recopying and methodical omission abounds.<lb/>
Figures 11 and 12 collate corresponding entries in the second subject chapter.<lb/>
