<p>ing exemplary literary works from writers of her time, it makes sense that she<lb/>
would have fueled anticipation for coming titles. The longer timeline involved in<lb/>
producing translations of these foreign works also might have factored into the<lb/>
months-long gap between teaser chapter publication in <hi>Sur</hi> and full-length book<lb/>
