The two Horatian satires that follow <hi>To Arbuthnot</hi> have the same illustrations<lb/>
as in the separate quarto, Satire II.i bringing its picture of Pope’s life to a close<lb/>
with the ‘<hi>UNI ÆQVVS VIRTVTI ATQ. EIVS AMICI</hi>’ vignette. The Donne<lb/>
