</p>
<p>Although this latter chapter is entirely written on wove stock in keeping with the paper used for the majority of the third volume, variants in the chapter’s numbering (<note>see table 3</note>) reveal that it also had been extensively revised, as has already been noted, in part, by the Clarendon editors.<sup>126</sup><lb/>
